{"data":[{"name":"79:1","price":"1. Par les arracheurs (des âmes) avec violence !","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰزِعَٰتِ غَرۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5713,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:2","price":"2. Et par ceux qui les cueillent avec douceur !","arabic":"وَٱلنَّٰشِطَٰتِ نَشۡطٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5714,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:3","price":"3. Par ceux qui naviguent librement,","arabic":"وَٱلسَّٰبِحَٰتِ سَبۡحٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5715,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:4","price":"4. puis courent et devancent,","arabic":"فَٱلسَّٰبِقَٰتِ سَبۡقٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5716,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:5","price":"5. pour mieux gérer les affaires !","arabic":"فَٱلۡمُدَبِّرَٰتِ أَمۡرٗا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5717,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:6","price":"6. Le jour où retentira (le premier son du Cor),","arabic":"يَوۡمَ تَرۡجُفُ ٱلرَّاجِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5718,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:7","price":"7. et que suivra le second (son du Cor),","arabic":"تَتۡبَعُهَا ٱلرَّادِفَةُ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5719,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:8","price":"8. des cœurs, ce jour-là, seront saisis de frayeur,","arabic":"قُلُوبٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ وَاجِفَةٌ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5720,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:9","price":"9. et des regards saisis d’humilité.","arabic":"أَبۡصَٰرُهَا خَٰشِعَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5721,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:10","price":"10. « Serons-nous donc, demanderont-ils, ramenés à notre vie sur terre,","arabic":"يَقُولُونَ أَءِنَّا لَمَرۡدُودُونَ فِي ٱلۡحَافِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5722,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:11","price":"11. alors même que nous ne serons plus qu’ossements rongés? »","arabic":"أَءِذَا كُنَّا عِظَٰمٗا نَّخِرَةٗ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5723,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:12","price":"12. « Ce serait donc, diront-ils, un retour où nous serions perdants ! »","arabic":"قَالُواْ تِلۡكَ إِذٗا كَرَّةٌ خَاسِرَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5724,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:13","price":"13. Il n’y aura qu’un seul Cri,","arabic":"فَإِنَّمَا هِيَ زَجۡرَةٞ وَٰحِدَةٞ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5725,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:14","price":"14. et les voilà tous qui se réveillent à la surface de la terre !","arabic":"فَإِذَا هُم بِٱلسَّاهِرَةِ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5726,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:15","price":"15. L’histoire de Moïse t’est-elle parvenue ?","arabic":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ مُوسَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5727,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:16","price":"16. Son Seigneur l’appela dans la vallée sacrée de Touwâ en lui disant :","arabic":"إِذۡ نَادَىٰهُ رَبُّهُۥ بِٱلۡوَادِ ٱلۡمُقَدَّسِ طُوًى","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5728,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:17","price":"17. « Va trouver Pharaon, car il a transgressé ! ","arabic":"ٱذۡهَبۡ إِلَىٰ فِرۡعَوۡنَ إِنَّهُۥ طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5729,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:18","price":"18. Dis-lui : “Ne voudrais-tu pas te purifier","arabic":"فَقُلۡ هَل لَّكَ إِلَىٰٓ أَن تَزَكَّىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5730,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:19","price":"19. et me laisser te guider vers ton Seigneur que tu craindras alors ?” »","arabic":"وَأَهۡدِيَكَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ فَتَخۡشَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5731,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:20","price":"20. (Moïse) fit voir (à Pharaon) le plus grand prodige.","arabic":"فَأَرَىٰهُ ٱلۡأٓيَةَ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5732,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:21","price":"21. Mais celui-ci le tint pour mensonge et désobéit (à Allah),","arabic":"فَكَذَّبَ وَعَصَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5733,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:22","price":"22. puis se détourna persistant dans la mécréance.","arabic":"ثُمَّ أَدۡبَرَ يَسۡعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5734,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:23","price":"23. Il rassembla (les siens) et fit cette déclaration :","arabic":"فَحَشَرَ فَنَادَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5735,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:24","price":"24. « Je suis votre seigneur le plus haut ! »","arabic":"فَقَالَ أَنَا۠ رَبُّكُمُ ٱلۡأَعۡلَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5736,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:25","price":"25. Allah sévit contre lui par le supplice exemplaire de l’autre monde et de la vie ici-bas.","arabic":"فَأَخَذَهُ ٱللَّهُ نَكَالَ ٱلۡأٓخِرَةِ وَٱلۡأُولَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5737,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:26","price":"26. Il y a certes là une leçon à méditer par quiconque craint (Allah).","arabic":"إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَعِبۡرَةٗ لِّمَن يَخۡشَىٰٓ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5738,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:27","price":"27. Êtes-vous plus difficiles à créer que le ciel qu’Il a édifié ? ","arabic":"ءَأَنتُمۡ أَشَدُّ خَلۡقًا أَمِ ٱلسَّمَآءُۚ بَنَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5739,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:28","price":"28. Il en a élevé bien haut la voûte et a su en parfaire la forme.","arabic":"رَفَعَ سَمۡكَهَا فَسَوَّىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5740,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:29","price":"29. Il en a rendu la nuit obscure et en a fait briller le jour.","arabic":"وَأَغۡطَشَ لَيۡلَهَا وَأَخۡرَجَ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5741,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:30","price":"30. La terre, après cela, Il l’a nivelée.","arabic":"وَٱلۡأَرۡضَ بَعۡدَ ذَٰلِكَ دَحَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5742,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:31","price":"31. Il en a fait sortir eaux et pâturages.","arabic":"أَخۡرَجَ مِنۡهَا مَآءَهَا وَمَرۡعَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5743,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:32","price":"32. Les montagnes, Il les a implantées,","arabic":"وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5744,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:33","price":"33. pour vos besoins à vous et à ceux de vos bestiaux.","arabic":"مَتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5745,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:34","price":"34. Mais quand se produira le plus grand des cataclysmes,","arabic":"فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلطَّآمَّةُ ٱلۡكُبۡرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5746,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:35","price":"35. le jour où l’homme se souviendra de ce tout ce qu’il s’est employé à accomplir,","arabic":"يَوۡمَ يَتَذَكَّرُ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَا سَعَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5747,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:36","price":"36. et que l’Enfer sera mis en évidence devant quiconque peut voir,","arabic":"وَبُرِّزَتِ ٱلۡجَحِيمُ لِمَن يَرَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5748,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:37","price":"37. alors, celui qui se sera livré à la démesure,","arabic":"فَأَمَّا مَن طَغَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5749,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:38","price":"38. et qui aura préféré la vie en ce bas monde,","arabic":"وَءَاثَرَ ٱلۡحَيَوٰةَ ٱلدُّنۡيَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5750,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:39","price":"39. aura pour seul refuge l’Enfer !","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5751,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:40","price":"40. Quant à celui que le statut suprême de son Seigneur (faisait trembler) de crainte, (celui qui) s’interdisait de succomber aux passions,","arabic":"وَأَمَّا مَنۡ خَافَ مَقَامَ رَبِّهِۦ وَنَهَى ٱلنَّفۡسَ عَنِ ٱلۡهَوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5752,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:41","price":"41. le Paradis sera son séjour.","arabic":"فَإِنَّ ٱلۡجَنَّةَ هِيَ ٱلۡمَأۡوَىٰ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5753,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:42","price":"42. Ils t’interrogent au sujet de l’Heure : « Quand va-t-elle enfin venir ? »","arabic":"يَسۡـَٔلُونَكَ عَنِ ٱلسَّاعَةِ أَيَّانَ مُرۡسَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5754,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:43","price":"43. Comment saurais-tu y trouver réponse ? ","arabic":"فِيمَ أَنتَ مِن ذِكۡرَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5755,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:44","price":"44. C’est de ton Seigneur que relève son terme.","arabic":"إِلَىٰ رَبِّكَ مُنتَهَىٰهَآ","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5756,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:45","price":"45. Tu n’es là, (quant à toi), que pour avertir quiconque l’appréhende.","arabic":"إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُنذِرُ مَن يَخۡشَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5757,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"},{"name":"79:46","price":"46. Le jour où ils la verront, ce sera comme s’ils n’étaient restés (sur terre) qu’un après-midi ou une matinée !","arabic":"كَأَنَّهُمۡ يَوۡمَ يَرَوۡنَهَا لَمۡ يَلۡبَثُوٓاْ إِلَّا عَشِيَّةً أَوۡ ضُحَىٰهَا","category":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at"],"ayahNumber":5758,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"fr"}],"chapter":["79 (An-Nazi'at)","An-Nazi'at","Surah An-Nazi'at","Chapter An-Nazi'at","Nazi'at","Surah Nazi'at","Chapter Nazi'at","An Nazi'at","Surah An Nazi'at","Chapter An Nazi'at","Surah 79","Chapter 79","Those Who Pull Out","النازعات"]}